yeah finally i can do this. yes this project can do with jade template engine with following step:
1. install jade -> npm install jade
2. modify webpack config with adding jade extension

`resolve: {
    // ensure loader extensions match
    extensions: ['','.ts','.js','.json','.css','.html','.jade']
  },`
1. adding jade to loader

`
{ test: /\.jade$/,  loader: 'jade' }
`

for implementation just call by require like this

`
@Component({
    template: require('!jade!./your_file.jade')(),
`
work for me :)

